nget/EE6350_S14/ClassD_SKSS/index.html\">here</a>.\r\n\r\nI have been working on a circuit drawing tool for exporting publication quality graphics. It\'s currently in alpha but you can try it out <a href=\"http://bitbucket.org/siddharthshekar/ycircuit\">here</a>.'),(5301,912,'awards','<p class=\"h2\">Publications</p>\r\n\"Measurement of DNA Translocation Dynamics in a Solid-State Nanopore at 100 ns Temporal Resolution.\" <b>Shekar S.</b>, Niedzwiecki D., Chien C.-C., Ong P., Fleischer D. A., Lin J., Rosenstein J. K., Drndic M., Shepard K. L., <i>Nano Letters</i>, 2016 (<a href=\"http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/acs.nanolett.6b01661\">Link</a>)'),(5302,912,'current_position',''),(5303,912,'email_address','sshekar@ee.columbia.edu'),(5304,912,'linkedin',''),(5305,912,'telephone',''),(5306,912,'address',''),(5307,912,'_pods_photo','a:1:{i:0;i:913;}'),(5310,912,'photo','913'),(5311,914,'zenofwp_menulogic_menuselect','0'),(5312,914,'_edit_last','1'),(5313,914,'_edit_lock','1491503145:1'),(5314,915,'_wp_attached_file','2017/04/jsherman.png'),(5315,915,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:375;s:6:\"height\";i:500;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2017/04/jsherman.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:12:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"jsherman-80x80.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:80;s:6:\"height\";i:80;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"jsherman-225x300.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:225;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"widget\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:18:\"jsherman-36x36.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:36;s:6:\"height\";i:36;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"square\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"jsherman-180x180.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:180;s:6:\"height\";i:180;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:8:\"featured\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"jsherman-375x430.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:375;s:6:\"height\";i:430;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"portfolio\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"jsherman-375x400.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:375;s:6:\"height