_textblock]\r\n[/av_one_full]\r\n\r\n[av_toggle_container initial=\'0\' mode=\'accordion\' sort=\'\']\r\n[av_toggle title=\'Abstract\' tags=\'\']\r\nWe present the first experimental high-frequency measurements of graphene field-effect transistors (GFETs), demonstrating an fT of 14.7 GHz for a 500-nm-length device. We also present detailed measurement and analysis of velocity saturation in GFETs, demonstrating the potential for velocities approaching 108 cm/sec and the effect of an ambipolar channel on current-voltage characteristics.\r\n[/av_toggle]\r\n\r\n[/av_toggle_container]','RF performance of top-gated, zero-bandgap graphene field-effect transistors','','publish','open','open','','rf-performance-of-top-gated-zero-bandgap-graphene-field-effect-transistors','','','2017-04-04 18:26:15','2017-04-04 18:26:15','',0,'http://bioee.academicwebpages.com/?p=391',0,'post','',0),(392,1,'2017-04-04 17:58:22','2017-04-04 17:58:22','','iedm_final_v5','','inherit','open','closed','','iedm_final_v5','','','2017-04-04 17:58:22','2017-04-04 17:58:22','',391,'http://bioee.academicwebpages.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/iedm_final_v5.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(393,1,'2017-04-04 17:59:29','2017-04-04 17:59:29','I. Meric, N. Baklitskaya, P. Kim, and K. L. Shepard, \"<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/iedm_final_v5.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">RF performance of top-gated, zero-bandgap graphene field-effect transistors</a>,\" International Electron Devices Meeting, 2008.','RF performance of top-gated, zero-bandgap graphene field-effect transistors','','inherit','closed','closed','','391-revision-v1','','','2017-04-04 17:59:29','2017-04-04 17:59:29','',391,'http://bioee.academicwebpages.com/391-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(394,1,'2017-04-04 18:05:20','2017-04-04 18:05:20','[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\nI. Meric, N. Baklitskaya, P. Kim, and K. L. Shepard, \"<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/iedm_final_v5.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">RF performan